<body>
The most basic of all cold attack spells, the caster holds out a hand,<br>
palm upright, and using a few words of power forces the air between the<br>
palm and the caster's opponent to became painfully, destructively cold. <br>
The victim can suffer intense pain and damage from the chilling touch if<br>
the caster is proficient enough in the nature of the spell.<br>
